{"tid":246390,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"發唔發覺啲人越食越多藥","createTime":"2017-05-17T03:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T14:50:50.000Z","uid":64743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b05a1eabcea28e75544c0c7fd5da973970b618e5","tid":246390,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"我發覺香港人係又食藥唔係又食藥<br />\n乜事都冇就食藥打底<br />\n流少少鼻水又食藥<br />\n真係病就緊係食藥啦<br />\n頭痛又食藥<br />\n食完仲係痛食多2粒<br />\n再痛 食到唔痛為止<br />\n公司個阿姐頭痛<br />\n話食藥<br />\n我問佢食幾多粒<br />\n8粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲人係咪覺得藥係補品黎"},{"pid":"de0488c9809a570fb860b51b3cd03c473c167841","tid":246390,"uid":55991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:39:47.000Z","msg":"呢個真 d人都痴撚線<br />\n你少少病食成7粒8粒拓咩<br />\n訓多d教 飲多杯水好撚過啦<br />\n係唔係都食 好似食仙丹咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37e32924584b761522a77c59257e663cf63f113","tid":246390,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"係又食必理病 唔係又食必理痛"},{"pid":"37627e0a4a0238113bcae4153668f2921afa9f96","tid":246390,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:40:39.000Z","msg":"所以而家d病菌好勁，適應曬d藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b076a4f7947586eeee6483fca8d56fcbb629ecfe","tid":246390,"uid":55991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個真 d人都痴撚線<br />\n你少少病食成7粒8粒拓咩<br />\n訓多d教 飲多杯水好撚過啦<br />\n係唔係都食 好似食仙丹咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見過個細路只係話頭痛 佢呀媽即刻拎幾粒藥「則」佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但明明只係個細路唔夠訓先頭痛咋嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4d36055f211e46937a4a4c7ceeffafb0972add","tid":246390,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:44:55.000Z","msg":"當你返工頭又痛，又要做嘢，就會食藥<br />\n<br />\n食極都唔好，越做嘢越痛，就只有食多幾粒藥"},{"pid":"e7b85fdfe4423d718898e53ae3fbcb3727e38152","tid":246390,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:47:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你返工頭又痛，又要做嘢，就會食藥<br />\n<br />\n食極都唔好，越做嘢越痛，就只有食多幾粒藥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實惡性循環黎<br />\n到你食隻藥指定既劑量都解決唔到<br />\n你就要睇醫生<br />\n再食只係令身體對隻藥越黎越冇反應"},{"pid":"6f24f152853b689d2848cd0e42706cabaf168e20","tid":246390,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T04:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係又食必理病 唔係又食必理痛</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5534e542d2b08c24206eef78af5c0c3236d9673","tid":246390,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T04:27:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係又食必理病 唔係又食必理痛</blockquote><br />\n我日日食2至6粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb0372f8e2aeaa36bc1b25f28fcc95e64482eec","tid":246390,"uid":47153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T04:44:25.000Z","msg":"呢個Post 啲人零醫學常識"},{"pid":"0ce5b7fda2326d14eaab72f9d3a7be6724090f64","tid":246390,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T05:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個Post 啲人零醫學常識</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153dc07c32c38fe98ac64f96bfa275a65edad49e","tid":246390,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T05:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個Post 啲人零醫學常識</blockquote><br />\n打句咁既廢話都唔顯得你有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef9d8429a4b8789f7c3f87405668d893a5a9d2b","tid":246390,"uid":91724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"好奈冇食過藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最重病都只係打下咳痴 過一日就冇事"},{"pid":"5adb6c8eef524249fdae7c0f080c70590d80ff87","tid":246390,"uid":91165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T05:45:30.000Z","msg":"介J增強抵抗力"},{"pid":"80309f91f7f43c8f7e3e30b413a0231c4b334d0c","tid":246390,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T05:52:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以而家d病菌好勁，適應曬d藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其武大部份藥都唔係抗菌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25c1cd51d5381c181babb43934866cf86f16538","tid":246390,"uid":16650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:42:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係又食必理病 唔係又食必理痛</blockquote><br />\n必理痛迅速溶解後會自然排出體外<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa27c6f11da907fcbb2c095ada07a298b416f4f","tid":246390,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:47:19.000Z","msg":"D人要搞壞自己身體都無佢符"},{"pid":"61d201fca8dad7a815ecf7744c3659c4f0404089","tid":246390,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所以而家d病菌好勁，適應曬d藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其武大部份藥都唔係抗菌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就咁喺貨架賣唔駛醫生開嘅藥多數只係用嚟舒緩症狀, 即係消炎止痛退燒嗰啲, 就算殺菌都只係好輕微或者外用殺癬嗰類<br />\n<br />\n真係內服抗菌抗病毒嘅藥要搵醫生或者註冊藥劑師開(依家大間萬寧, 屈臣氏都有藥劑師睇場撈埋呢條水)<br />\n<br />\n最大問題反而係醫病以外嘅途徑濫用抗生素(鄰國豬場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)搞到抗藥惡菌橫行"},{"pid":"ce988fc30aec8a14d49504407acbdabb907ce250","tid":246390,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>所以而家d病菌好勁，適應曬d藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其武大部份藥都唔係抗菌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就咁喺貨架賣唔駛醫生開嘅藥多數只係用嚟舒緩症狀, 即係消炎止痛退燒嗰啲, 就算殺菌都只係好輕微或者外用殺癬嗰類<br />\n<br />\n真係內服抗菌抗病毒嘅藥要搵醫生或者註冊藥劑師開(依家大間萬寧, 屈臣氏都有藥劑師睇場撈埋呢條水)<br />\n<br />\n最大問題反而係醫病以外嘅途徑濫用抗生素(鄰國豬場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)搞到抗藥惡菌橫行</blockquote><br />\n普通傷風感冒醫生都係開止痛止咳收鼻水，唔會有分別。"},{"pid":"2908da13a9e39eb44864ef73ccf24c684372db6f","tid":246390,"uid":52675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"藥箱都變成手飾箱"},{"pid":"fb2b62d736b966c61e38f1a520b90dd11b81d9e6","tid":246390,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T09:06:40.000Z","msg":"而家自殺都可以用必理痛喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b31d7c6f55ddf6b006e41ff02dcc9d0ac2c1da5","tid":246390,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:48:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家自殺都可以用必理痛喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有新出既無睡意配方 <br />\n内含豐富既維他命C <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e178a3a01d6660b2ff0d38074d415bebf1bfe019","tid":246390,"uid":14190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:50:50.000Z","msg":"有毒<br />\n傻仔先食<br />\n由得個身體去打係最好<br />\n<br />\n十幾年都冇病過"}]}